The paper also involves analyzing the sample complexity of the algorithms, which is a topic in theoretical computer science (cs.DS). The use of shift-and-invert preconditioning and the analysis of eigenvalue gaps suggests a connection to information theory (cs.IT) and control systems (cs.SY).
